[[File:Kree'arra chathead.png|left]]
'''Kree'arra''' is one of [[Armadyl]]'s most trusted generals. He is the most powerful of the surviving [[aviansie (race)|aviansie]], and leader to the forces of [[Armadyl's Eyrie]] in the [[God Wars Dungeon]].

In order to reach the encampment, players must first wield any [[crossbow (weapon)|crossbow]] along with a [[mithril grapple]]. A [[Ranged]] level of at least 70 is then required to navigate the chasm. To enter the boss room, players must use an [[ecumenical key]], or have slain 40<ref>35 for hard, 30 for elite, 25 for master and 15 kills for grandmaster for those who have unlocked the respective combat achievement tiers</ref> followers of Armadyl, with aviansie and their spiritual variants being his only followers within the dungeon.

Kree'arra can be seen yelling several battle cries in his chamber. However, unlike the other generals, his taunts are non-verbal.

